ADJDEF 1981 bee
MADJDEF 57 worker
MADJDEF 58 drone
MADJDEF 59 guard
NOUNDEF 2050 honey
MLIST 212 756 10 10
MLIST 212 757 10 10
MLIST 212 758 10 10
;
INUMBER 3002
NAME 2050
FOOD
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
ARTICLE SOME
PARAMETER1 100
IFPREVERB EAT -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO OTHERS %N sinks %h teeth into the sweet-smelling honey, and then recoils.
  ECHO PLAYER As you begin to taste the honey, you suddenly feel sick to your stomach!
  DAMAGEPLR POISON 15 The taste of the honey sours in your mouth.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TOUCH -1
  CLEARVERB
  EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
  ECHO OTHERS %N touches the honey, and is suddenly stuck in place.
  ECHO PLAYER Touching the honey, it grasps hold of your hand and you must pull it free.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LICK -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO OTHERS %N licks the honey, but then %h face starts to pale.
  ECHO PLAYER Licking the honey, you relish the sweet taste for only a moment, but the sourness overwhelms you.
  DAMAGEPLR BODYONLY 15 The sweet taste rapidly sours in your mouth.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO -1
  CLEARVERB
  EQUAL ROUNDTIME 20
  ECHO PLAYER Trying to enter the honey only gets you stuck in the acidic substance!
  DAMAGEPLR BURN 25 The honey starts to burn your skin.
  ECHO OTHERS %N presses up against the honey, you watch as it starts to burn %h skin.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GET -1
  EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
  ECHO PLAYER Picking up the sticky mass of honey, it coats your hands as you handle it.
  DAMAGEPLR BODYONLY 25 The sticky honey starts to burn your fingers.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB NIBBLE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO OTHERS As %N nibbles on the tasty honey, you notice %h lips start to burn.
  DAMAGEPLR BURN 20 As you nibble on the tasty honey, your lips start to burn.
ENDIF
;
MNUMBER 756
NAME worker
PART 00
