*DESCRIPTION_START
The bee is about ten times larger than normal. It is slow and methodical. Its
thorax is decorated in angry slashes of black and yellow. Your image is
reflected hundreds of times in its complex eyes.
*DESCRIPTION_END
BODY 100
EXTRABODY 80
ATTACK1 120
DEFENSE 120
STRATEGY 501
WEAPON 1636 1981 50
IMMUNITY 0
TREASURE 50
POISON 50 10
SPEED 8
SPECUSE 50
SPECUSES 2
SPECBASE 35
SPECDMG 25
SPECDMGTYPE SLASH
TEXX %s turns and aims its stinger at %s!
TEXE a worker bee bzzzzs in.
TEXD falls into a heap of yellow and black.
TEXM a worker bee bzzzzs
TEXA a worker bee flies right at
TEX1 a worker bee whirls upwards gaining speed.
TEX2 a worker bee drips honey.
TEX3 a worker bee buzzes your head.
TEXG a worker bee bzzzzs in.
SKINADJ 1981
SKINITEM 520 40
SKINITEM 509 40
GUARD 758
