NUMBER 10100
MONSTER_GROUP 212
REGION 0
NAME Hive, Central Chamber
INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS
*DESCRIPTION_START
This chamber is roughly circular, the walls being formed of octagonal shaped
pieces of honey-comb. The honey drips from almost all surfaces, coating
anything it touches. In the farthest reaches of the dark lie deeper pools
of utter black. Odd scratch marks marr the wet floor.
*DESCRIPTION_END
