MONSTER_GROUP 212
REGION 0
NAME Hive, Tiny Cell
INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS
*DESCRIPTION_START
This crowded little cell is hardly even a room. The walls are chewed up bits
of paper and plants tamped into place by the feet of the worker bees.
Each corner looks as if it could open into another large or small room, or
go nowhere are all.
